    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's not a cycle I want to break. It's just that the \"healing\" you're talking about feels like trying to put life back into something that's already finished. There's no \"self\" left to recover. There's just this empty weight. It feels like I'm just occupying a space that should have been empty a long time ago.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
